OL,3,CMental health failings contributed to
OL,4,Cmarine's death, inquest told
OL,6,FA failure to call a mental health
OL,7,Fconference for a marine recruit who
OL,8,Ftook his own life may have contributed
OL,9,Fto his death, an inquest in Exeter
OL,10,Fheard on Wednesday 3 July.
OL,12,FConnor Clark, 18, from Norfolk had
OL,13,Fused a duvet to scale a razor wire
OL,14,Ffence at the commando training centre
OL,15,F(CTC) in Lympstone, Devon, before
OL,16,Fbeing struck by a train on the morning
OL,17,Fof June 12 2021.
