OL,3,CMental health failings contributed to
OL,4,Cmarine's death, inquest told
OL,6,FThe teenager had made comments prior
OL,7,Fto his death about being called a
OL,8,F"failure" and the "worst recruit", and
OL,9,Fwas worried about losing weekend leave
OL,10,Ffor misplacing the blank firing
OL,11,Fadapter for his weapon.
OL,13,FA faulty CCTV camera was also
OL,14,Fhighlighted by the coroner Philip
OL,15,FSpinney, as he gave his conclusions
OL,16,Ftoday.
