OL,3,CMental health failings contributed to
OL,4,Cmarine's death, inquest told
OL,6,FHe said that, when Connor Clark
OL,7,Fpresented himself to sick bay with a
OL,8,Fwound that he had made worse himself,
OL,9,Fa referral should have been made as an
OL,10,Fincident of self-harm.
OL,12,FMr Spinney said this was a significant
OL,13,Ffailure that probably contributed to
OL,14,Fhis death.
OL,16,FOn the night that Connor Clark left
OL,17,Fthe camp, the night guards were two
OL,18,Fmembers short - with three on duty
OL,19,Finstead of five.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
