OL,6,FThe camera, which covered the area of
OL,7,Fthe fence where Connor had placed his
OL,8,Fbedding to climb, was said to
OL,9,Fsometimes malfunction.
OL,11,FThe inquest heard that it was
OL,12,Fstationary between 2.20am and 3.50am,
OL,13,Fand focused on an area of grass.
OL,15,FThe duvet was only confirmed when the
OL,16,FCCTV was reviewed later that morning.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
