OL,3,CMental health failings contributed to
OL,4,Cmarine's death, inquest told
OL,6,FThe coroner said he was aware that the
OL,7,FCCTV system at the base is under
OL,8,Freview, and that it is set up to guard
OL,9,Fagainst intruders and not to stop
OL,10,Fpeople from leaving.
OL,12,FHe said he did not consider it a
OL,13,Fsignificant factor towards the cause
OL,14,Fof Connor's death, but was critical of
OL,15,Fwhat happened when people realised he
OL,16,Fwas missing.
OL,18,FHe described the response as
OL,19,F"inadequate" with "no effective
OL,20,Fcoordinated approach", a lack of
OL,21,Findication of where he may be.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
