OL,6,FHe said there was evidence Mr Clark
OL,7,Fhad been looking for the piece of
OL,8,Fequipment as he was due to have an
OL,9,Finspection on the day he died.
OL,11,FIn his findings, Mr Spinney said Mr
OL,12,FClark had become "overwhelmed with the
OL,13,Fsituation" and had left the camp and
OL,14,Fended his life.
OL,16,F"I attach no criticism to the training
OL,17,Fstaff in relation to the loss of the
OL,18,Fblank firing attachment," he said.
