OL,3,CMental health failings contributed to
OL,4,Cmarine's death, inquest told
OL,6,F"I conclude that Connor losing his
OL,7,Fblank firing attachment probably
OL,8,Fcontributed more than minimally to the
OL,9,Fcause of his death."
OL,11,FMr Spinney said Mr Clark had died from
OL,12,Fmultiple severe injuries as he
OL,13,Frecorded a conclusion of suicide.
OL,15,FHilary Meredith Solicitors represented
OL,16,FConnor's mum Tracy at the inquest.
