OL,6,FFollowing the Coroner's conclusions
OL,7,Ftoday, Simon Quinn, Partner and Head
OL,8,Fof Military at Hilary Meredith
OL,9,FSolicitors said: "This is a very sad
OL,10,Fcase and unfortunately yet another
OL,11,Fexample of a young life lost too soon.
OL,13,F"After delays by the Ministry of
OL,14,FDefence (MoD) and following a long
OL,15,Fwait for an Inquest date, we welcome
OL,16,Fthe Coroner's conclusions and hope
OL,17,Fthat Mrs Clark is finally provided
OL,18,Fwith the answers she needed and
OL,19,Fdeserved.
OL,26,@qD@ROUuD@AOU
